Merge pull request #4 from vokal-isaac/master

Updates based on upstream review
Update podspec and README to reflect version 2.0.0 and call out removal of support for negative counts.
Make countLabelFont a property (proxy to the underlying count label's font property).
Add the `const` keyword to indicate that the constants are compile-time constant.
Use `static` to limit the scope of the constants to the compilation unit (basically, to the .m file) and prefix and export the default diameter to allow consumers of RKNotificationHub to use it.

Merge pull request #7 from petaren/UITableViewCell_support

Added support for UITableViewCell

Added support for UITableViewCell

UITableViewCell calls .backgroundColor = [UIColor whiteColor] on all
subviews when selected. This removes the red circle if the notification
hub is located in a tableviewcell.

I created a small subclass of UIView where I overrode
setBackgroundColor and only allows it to be set if the user(programmer)
explicitly has given his permission. The system cannot set the
backgroundcolor because it is not aware of this ivar.
